Subject: http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nobody's_Baby_(1937_film)
Object: Nobody's Baby is a 1937 American comedy film directed by Errol Taggart and written by Harold Law, Hal Yates and Pat C. Flick. The film stars Patsy Kelly, Lyda Roberti, Lynne Overman, Robert Armstrong, Rosina Lawrence and Don Alvarado. The film was released on April 23, 1937, by Metro-Goldwyn-Mayer.
